---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import MoodySplitView from '../components/diagrams/MoodySplitView.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Projects" showStars={false}>
  <header class="header">
    <h1 class="header-title">Projects</h1>
  </header>

  <div class="page-content">
    <div class="project-card">
      <div class="project-header">
        <img src="/img/moody-icon.png" alt="Moody App Icon" class="project-icon" />
        <div>
          <h2 class="project-title">Moody</h2>
          <p class="project-tagline">음악을 보여주는 디지털 액자</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p>Spotify와 연동되는 디지털 앨범 프레임. 지금 듣고 있는 음악의 앨범 아트를 10.1인치 IPS 디스플레이에 표시하고, 트랙 정보를 함께 보여줍니다.</p>

      <div class="project-wireframe">
        <MoodySplitView />
      </div>

      <div class="project-details">
        <div class="project-detail-group">
          <h3>담당</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>BLE 기반 디바이스 탐색 및 연결</li>
            <li>WiFi 네트워크 스캔 및 설정</li>
            <li>Spotify OAuth 2.0 (PKCE) 인증</li>
            <li>실시간 디바이스 상태 모니터링</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

      </div>

      <div class="project-tags-section">
        <div class="project-tags">
          <span class="project-tag">Flutter</span>
          <span class="project-tag">Riverpod</span>
          <span class="project-tag">BLE</span>
          <span class="project-tag">Spotify API</span>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
.project-card {
  border: 1px solid rgba(128, 128, 128, 0.15);
  border-radius: 8px;
  padding: 28px 32px;
  margin-top: 16px;
}

.project-header {
  display: flex;
  align-items: flex-start;
  gap: 16px;
  margin-bottom: 12px;
}

.project-icon {
  width: 64px;
  height: 64px;
  border-radius: 14px;
  object-fit: cover;
  margin: 0;
  flex-shrink: 0;
}

.project-title-row {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 10px;
}

.project-header h2 {
  margin: 0 !important;
  margin-top: 0 !important;
  font-size: 22px;
}

.project-badge {
  font-size: 12px;
  padding: 2px 10px;
  border-radius: 12px;
  background: rgba(129, 140, 248, 0.1);
  color: #818cf8;
  font-weight: 500;
  white-space: nowrap;
}

.project-tagline {
  color: #6b7886;
  font-size: 15px;
  margin-top: 2px;
  padding: 0;
}

.project-wireframe {
  margin: 24px 0;
  padding: 20px;
  border-radius: 8px;
  background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.03);
}

.project-details {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  gap: 20px;
  margin-top: 20px;
}

.project-detail-group h3 {
  font-size: 14px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  margin-top: 0;
  margin-bottom: 8px;
  border: none;
  padding: 0;
}

.project-detail-group ul {
  list-style: none;
  padding: 0;
}

.project-detail-group ul li {
  font-size: 14px;
  padding: 3px 0;
  color: #6b7886;
}

.project-detail-group ul li::before {
  content: "·";
  margin-right: 8px;
  font-weight: 700;
}

.project-tags-section {
  margin-top: 20px;
}

.project-tags {
  display: flex;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  gap: 6px;
}

.project-tag {
  font-size: 12px;
  padding: 3px 10px;
  border-radius: 4px;
  background: rgba(128, 128, 128, 0.08);
  color: #6b7886;
}

.project-links {
  margin-top: 20px;
}

.project-link {
  font-size: 14px;
  font-weight: 600;
  color: #003fff;
  text-decoration: none;
}

.project-link:hover {
  color: #0036c7;
}

@media screen and (max-width: 768px) {
  .project-card {
    padding: 20px;
  }
  .project-details {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
  }
}

:global(body[data-theme="dark"]) .project-card {
  border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
}

:global(body[data-theme="dark"]) .project-wireframe {
  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02);
}

:global(body[data-theme="dark"]) .project-tagline,
:global(body[data-theme="dark"]) .project-detail-group ul li,
:global(body[data-theme="dark"]) .project-tag {
  color: #908caa;
}

:global(body[data-theme="dark"]) .project-tag {
  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
}

:global(body[data-theme="dark"]) .project-badge {
  background: rgba(129, 140, 248, 0.15);
}

:global(body[data-theme="dark"]) .project-link {
  color: #ff5277;
}

:global(body[data-theme="dark"]) .project-link:hover {
  color: #ff2957;
}
</style>
